<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1-ạảʿid̊ ʿalayã ḥadītẖaⁿạ
 yaḥ̊lū lisam̊ʿī ṣadāhu
 ʿan̊ sayĩdī waḥabībī
 wagẖāsilī bidimāhu

[V2]
 2- ʿin̊damā jāʾa ại̹laẙnā
 ṭif̊lạaⁿ wadīʿaⁿạ fī midẖ̊wad̊
 mā lahu fī ạl̊baẙti mah̊duⁿ
 walạ makānuⁿ līūlad̊

[V3]
 3- ạảʿid̊ ʿalayã ḥadītẖa
 ạl̊fādī ạl̊majīdi ạl̊ḥabībi
 wās̊rid̊ waradĩd̊ kalạma
 ạlsĩf̊ri ạllãdẖīdẖi ạl̊ʿajībi

[V4]
 4- ʿan̊ kẖāliqi ạl̊kaẘni lamãạ
 wāfay̱ dīāra ạlsẖãqāʾi
 wajāla fīhā muhānaⁿạ
 mus̊tah̊dafaⁿạ lil̊ʿanāʾi</lyrics>
<title>ạ̉ʿd ʿly ḥdytẖạaⁿ</title>
